## Phase 6: Multi-Strategy Coordination

### Signal Conflict Resolution

```python
class SignalConflictResolver:
    async def resolve_conflicts(self, signals: List[Signal]) -> Optional[Signal]:
        buy_signals = [s for s in signals if s.signal_type == SignalType.BUY]
        sell_signals = [s for s in signals if s.signal_type == SignalType.SELL]
        
        if buy_signals and sell_signals:
            buy_conf = sum(s.confidence * s.weight for s in buy_signals)
            sell_conf = sum(s.confidence * s.weight for s in sell_signals)
            
            # 10% bias threshold to avoid flip-flopping
            if buy_conf > sell_conf * 1.1:
                return self._aggregate(buy_signals)
            elif sell_conf > buy_conf * 1.1:
                return self._aggregate(sell_signals)
            else:
                return Signal(signal_type=SignalType.HOLD)  # Too close
```

