## Phase 7: Pre-Trade Compliance

### 7 Mandatory Checks

| Check | Description | Rejection Reason |
|-------|-------------|------------------|
| Restricted Securities | Internal restricted list | "Restricted security" |
| Hard-to-Borrow | Reg SHO share locate | "HTB: No shares to locate" |
| Insider Blackout | Earnings/MNPI periods | "Insider blackout period" |
| 13D Filing | 5% ownership threshold | "13D filing triggered" |
| Pattern Day Trading | 4 trades in 5 days, $25K min | "PDT limit reached" |
| Concentration Limits | Position concentration | "Concentration exceeded" |
| Watch List | Compliance monitoring | Alert compliance team |

