## Phase 9: Circuit Breakers

### 5 Protection Mechanisms

| Mechanism | Threshold | Action |
|-----------|-----------|--------|
| Manual Kill Switch | User-activated | HALT all trading |
| Order Rate Limit | >10/second | HALT |
| Daily Loss Limit | -2% | HALT + emergency close |
| Drawdown Limit | -5% from high | HALT + emergency close |
| Warning Level | 80% of limits | WARNING status |

```python
class CircuitBreakerLevel(Enum):
    NORMAL = "normal"       # 🟢 All systems operational
    WARNING = "warning"     # 🟡 Approaching limits (80%)
    CAUTION = "caution"     # 🟠 Limit breached
    HALT = "halt"           # 🔴 Trading stopped
    EMERGENCY = "emergency" # ⚫ System shutdown
```

