## Position Management Authority

**ONLY CentralRiskManager can update positions.**

```python
async def update_position(self, symbol: str, side: str, quantity: float, price: float):
    if side == 'buy':
        self.positions[symbol] += quantity
        self.available_cash -= quantity * price
    else:
        self.positions[symbol] -= quantity
        self.available_cash += quantity * price
    
    await self._notify_position_change(...)
```

