## PROHIBITED Patterns

### ❌ Bypassing Authorization

```python
# WRONG: No authorization check
async def execute_trade(self, signal):
    await self.broker.place_order(...)  # ❌ PROHIBITED
```

### ✅ Correct Authorization Flow

```python
# CORRECT: Full authorization flow
async def execute_trade(self, request):
    auth = await self.risk_manager.authorize_trading_decision(request)
    if auth.authorized:
        result = await self._execute_authorized(auth)
        await self.risk_manager.on_execution_complete(auth.id, result)
```

