## MANDATORY Requirements

1. All strategies register with StrategyManager
2. All trades pass 7 compliance checks
3. ALL trades require CentralRiskManager authorization
4. Circuit breaker check before every execution
5. ONLY CentralRiskManager updates positions
6. Complete audit trail of all decisions

